{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce Mandatory National Service or Training for Youth Offenders.",
        "additional_details": "We want the Government to introduce a mandatory program of military-style training or national service for youth offenders. This should focus on instilling discipline, personal responsibility, and respect for the law, providing a structured alternative to the current failing youth justice system.",
